HEADWORD: Toreutic
<hw>To*reu"tic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <?/ belonging
to work in relief.]</ety> <fld>(Sculp.)</fld> <def>In relief; pertaining
